However, the focus on sparsity and optimization techniques suggests that the paper is most likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT) or Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the use of mathematical proofs and analysis suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the Statistics (cs.SI) sub-category.
